description: A weighted, directed network representing the neural network.

qares.question: what nodes link with "237"?
which node has the highest degree in the graph?
qares.query: SELECT ?e1 WHERE { m.grap@en4kta graph.property.contain_nodes ?e1. e1? node.property.degree ?e2} ORDER BY DESC(?e2) LIMIT 1

qares.question: what is the node with the lowest centrality in the graph?
qares.query: SELECT ?e1 WHERE { m.grap@en4kta graph.property.contain_nodes ?e1. e1? node.property.degree_centrality ?e2} ORDER BY (?e2) LIMIT 1

qares.question: what is the node with the highest centrality that links with "230"?
qares.query: SELECT ?e1 WHERE { m.node@230 node.property.link_with ?e1. e1? node.property.degree_centrality ?e2} ORDER BY DESC(?e2) LIMIT 1

qares.question: what is the node with the lowest centrality in community 1?
qares.query: SELECT ?e1 WHERE { m.comm@rth78o community.property.contain_nodes ?e1. e1? node.property.degree_centrality ?e2} ORDER BY (?e2) LIMIT 1
